2 unit(s) Hard Boiled Egg
8 tbsp Hummus
1 cup Cheese Curds
2 unit(s) Gala Apple
6 unit(s) Celery
56 g Dried Cranberries
2 unit(s) Honey

Halve eggs, then season with salt and pepper. Core, then cut apple into 1/2-inch wedges. Cut celery in half lengthwise.

Divide hummus, eggs, celery, cranberries, cheese curds and apples slices between plates. Drizzle honey over the apple slices.